{"tid":1028323,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［政治笑話］李科員在北京飯店","createTime":"2019-02-19T11:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T12:10:46.000Z","uid":19408,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb2be6931d89c237372ffc1aff6ed6d772c688e","tid":1028323,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T11:53:58.000Z","msg":"李科員到北京旅行，住進了北京飯店的四人間，此前入住的三個人已經互相認識，他們喝酒聊天，大聲喧曄，還不停地講著政治笑話，李科員想趕快睡覺，於是想出一招。<br />\n他走出房間，對旅店服務員說：<br />\n「十分鐘之後，往22號房間送一壺茶。」<br />\n說完之後他回到房間，稍坐片刻，對著一隻煙灰缸說道：<br />\n「22號房間，送一壼茶。」<br />\n幾分鐘後，服務員馬上端著一壺茶進來了，那三個講政治笑話的人頓時失聲，房間死一般的沈寂，李科員也終於得以入睡。<br />\n第二天一早醒來，李科員發現另外三個人都不見了。他走出房間，問服務員:<br />\n「那三個人呢？」<br />\n「這個你不需要知道。」<br />\n李科員ー下子很緊張:「那我有事嗎？」<br />\n服務員說:「你沒說過什麼。另外，書記對你讓他們閉嘴那招很贊賞。」"},{"pid":"b33427664240eeeefc2f1da0bdd54883008b3d3d","tid":1028323,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac75d4fba26f6844c672ee1dd3f69927f0791f0","tid":1028323,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd97919063a9d32eda27ad026d82df3e8154928","tid":1028323,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ea393c0cede6a4e7ce5a9dcac04b2ba00ad513","tid":1028323,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d246f9142a993cf6199b7ec02d39e1b401bb7ea9","tid":1028323,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}